      "comment": "ROWEINER'S DANCE (4) has three wins and two minor placings from six runs this campaign. Found one better last start at Townsville over 1000m after being prominent upon straightening. This is an easier assignment and he can return to the winners' list. NORTHERNONTAP (7) finished fifth last start over 1200m at Townsville after racing on the pace for much of the way. Will go forward and is expected to be in the finish. HELLISH (2) raced on the speed when resuming last start but peaked on his run on straightening and faded to finish eighth over 1000m at Townsville. Will make his presence felt. FAMILY STAR (1) showed good early speed and raced on the pace last start before fading to finish fourth, beaten 3 lengths, over 1000m at Townsville. Has ability and a bold showing is expected.",
